                <head>No. 135.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Señor <persName
                            type="to">Flores</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilmington, Del.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-07-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 4, 1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Understanding from your announcement of amnesty that Santos is now at liberty to
                    come home, the Iroquois will be recalled.</p>
                <p>Show this to Mr. Adee.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>T. F. BAYARD.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
